<!-- can be changed via merge in the assembly -->
      <para>
        The following overview describes the process of deploying &productnameshort; raw disk image
        on a virtual machine.
      </para>
    </abstract>
  </info>
  <procedure>
    <step>
      <para>
        Download the &productnameshort; raw disk image.
      </para>
    </step>
    <step>
      <para>
        If needed, prepare the configuration device for &ignition; and &combustion;.
      </para>
    </step>
    <step>
      <para>
        Create the virtual machine based on the downloaded raw disk image.
      </para>
    </step>
    <step>
      <para>
        Register your system.
      </para>
    </step>
  </procedure>
  <para>
    Each step is described in detail in the following sections.
